WEBVTT

00:05.964 --> 00:08.173
THIS PROGRAM IS LOOSELY BASED
ON ACTUAL EVENTS.

00:08.258 --> 00:11.010
CHARACTERS AND EVENTS
WERE ADAPTED FOR DRAMATIC EFFECT.

00:14.431 --> 00:16.516
[tap squeaks]

00:20.478 --> 00:21.688
Hey!

00:22.480 --> 00:23.648
Is anybody there?

00:25.567 --> 00:27.193
Take it easy, politician!

00:27.986 --> 00:30.321
What's going on? Are you lonely?

00:30.405 --> 00:32.073
[Rangel] There's no water. I'm thirsty.

00:32.156 --> 00:33.700
Better get used to it, pal.

00:34.117 --> 00:37.078
Room service gets really bad
on weekends, if you know what I mean.

00:37.579 --> 00:39.164
Few employees around...

00:39.247 --> 00:41.458
Almost no one's here to pick up after you.

00:42.208 --> 00:44.836
Can you imagine if something nasty
was to happen to you?

00:45.336 --> 00:47.922
It'd be a long time
before they found you.

00:48.006 --> 00:49.340
[he laughs]

00:49.424 --> 00:50.550
[Ruffo] <i>At that moment,</i>

00:50.633 --> 00:54.387
<i>the destiny of the entire country</i>
<i>was in the hands of one man:</i>

00:54.471 --> 00:55.930
<i>João Pedro Rangel.</i>

00:56.848 --> 00:58.475
<i>If he opened his mouth...</i>

00:58.933 --> 01:00.435
<i>Brasília was fucked.</i>

01:01.478 --> 01:04.272
<i>Rigo and the Prosecutor's Office</i>
<i>played their first card.</i>

01:04.938 --> 01:06.900
<i>They sent the guy to hell</i>

01:06.983 --> 01:10.987
<i>to see if the devil could convince him</i>
<i>to accept a plea bargain.</i>

01:11.071 --> 01:14.949
<i>It was a good try</i>
<i>and it scared a lot of people.</i>

01:15.033 --> 01:17.827
Agostini, if you don't get
my husband out of jail,

01:18.453 --> 01:21.039
I'm going to be the one who blabs.
Is that clear enough for you?

01:21.706 --> 01:23.124
Do we understand each other?

01:24.751 --> 01:28.338
I'm not the one who needs
to understand, Samira.

01:29.923 --> 01:30.924
Ah!

01:32.133 --> 01:34.886
Then exactly who
has to understand it, Agostini?

01:34.969 --> 01:35.970
Explain it.

01:36.805 --> 01:38.556
[Mário] The state penitentiary?

01:39.349 --> 01:40.892
[Agostini] And the worst one there.

01:40.975 --> 01:42.435
Hand-picked, too.

01:42.519 --> 01:43.937
That's a low blow.

01:44.729 --> 01:46.105
They want him to crack.

01:46.439 --> 01:48.066
There's nothing I can do about it.

01:48.608 --> 01:52.987
João Pedro doesn't have the strength
for it. He's not prepared for Jaraguara.

01:53.071 --> 01:56.407
No one is prepared for Jaraguara.

01:56.491 --> 01:59.160
If they break him, it will all go to hell.

02:00.912 --> 02:02.413
[Mário breathes heavily]

02:02.497 --> 02:04.040
In Jaraguara...

02:05.125 --> 02:06.459
he will either break...

02:07.043 --> 02:08.294
or he dies.

02:09.128 --> 02:11.965
[Ruffo] <i>Rigo couldn't leave the guy</i>
<i>in Jaraguara too long.</i>

02:13.550 --> 02:15.969
<i>Someone might kill the prick.</i>

02:16.052 --> 02:18.138
<i>A dead man of that magnitude...</i>

02:18.555 --> 02:20.348
<i>would be a huge damn problem.</i>

02:21.766 --> 02:23.977
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

